      "body" : "I used the below instruction from http://www.peercointalk.org/index.php?topic=798.0 link:\r\n\r\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n# Get db4.8 source, compile and install\r\nwget http://download.oracle.com/berkeley-db/db-4.8.30.NC.tar.gz\r\ntar -xzvf db-4.8.30.NC.tar.gz\r\ncd db-4.8.30.NC/build_unix\r\n../dist/configure --enable-cxx\r\nmake\r\nsudo make install\r\n\r\n# Tell your system where to find db4.8\r\nexport BDB_INCLUDE_PATH=\"/usr/local/BerkeleyDB.4.8/include\"\r\nexport BDB_LIB_PATH=\"/usr/local/BerkeleyDB.4.8/lib\"\r\nln -s /usr/local/BerkeleyDB.4.8/lib/libdb-4.8.so /usr/lib/libdb-4.8.so\r\nln -s /usr/local/BerkeleyDB.4.8/lib/libdb_cxx-4.8.so /usr/lib/libdb_cxx-4.8.so\r\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\nUnfortunately, the result is the same.",
